I don't think that would work because of the massive amount of material already concerning the entity. Changing the nature or "existence" of the entity would require producing enough material to over-ride all the material that already exists.

I think of it as analogous to making Cthulu into a Hello Kitty style nice monster. That's been done and will continue to be done, but a lot of Cthulu's fans think that is total bullshit and the general perception of Cthulu remains true to its origin. Making the 582 entity harmless or non-existent would mean killing the larger cultural myth that powers it.







